Character Abstract Attack - Player uses weapon attacks, Enemy has their own attacks, bandit shoots a lot of magic projectiles, archer shoots arrows, knight does contact damage
Character Abstract Check - each character checks for different conditions
Character Abstract Update - each character updates their own position and different things such as their attacks
Character Abstract Draw - all character has slightly different draw state, so splitting in to own implementation is easier
Character Abstract Destroy - Enemy just cease to exist when die, player destroy means that the player lost the game.
Enemy Virtual Move - enemy can have their own same movement set, and can be added on later as specific to class.
